@Homeji_Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7166
@AccessToken = replace-with-supabase-access-token

GET {{Homeji_Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{Homeji_Api_HostAddress}}/api/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
